<title>Citykart Code Analysis Exam</title>
<style>
body { font-family: 'Segoe UI', Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333; max-width: 800px; margin: auto; padding: 20px;}
h1 { color: #004085; border-bottom: 2px solid #004085; padding-bottom: 10px; }
h2 { color: #333; font-size: 1.2em; margin-top: 30px; }
pre { background-color: #f4f4f4; padding: 15px; border-radius: 5px; font-family: Consolas, monospace; color: #d63384; border-left: 4px solid #004085;}
.bug { color: #dc3545; font-weight: bold; }
.fix { color: #198754; font-weight: bold; }
hr { border: 0; border-top: 1px solid #eee; margin: 30px 0; }
</style>
